Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日已经是姐姐了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你姐姐 你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.90,0:00:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈还在世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也还很温柔的那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时我和妈妈做了约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常重要的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.60,0:00:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧不知道退了没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体温貌似跟明日差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.50,0:01:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.90,0:01:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去送报纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.60,0:01:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.40,0:01:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 那门不开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.90,0:01:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冒着大雨勉强送报纸 感冒加重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.70,0:01:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.70,0:01:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有句话不是说“病随心情时好时坏”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.40,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行 快去休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.10,0:03:34.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}感冒和约定和妈妈的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 粥已经好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢了 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当心别烫着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吃极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有食欲就没什么大问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日不吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在还不吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出过汗了 得擦干净换套衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗 要不要再放点冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,量好体温然后安静睡一觉就会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔患患感冒看起来也不是坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 得快点好起来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则明日又要担心了 这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经全好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真是替你担心 这样最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始还望你继续多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得加把劲把耽误的工作量给补上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不在家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 水开着没关 怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 这是干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房东先生 请把明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我一起把明日送去医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 明日 觉得冷吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总不能从这一直抱着她跑去医院啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何我一点都没察觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日也感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到病倒为止都忍着不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日 没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是感冒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我这么说的妈妈上了救护车以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再也没有从医院回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来需要住院一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 有劳医生费心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就有交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得让病人的姐姐先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 至少今晚让她留下陪夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 明日 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想变坚强 想变得更坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想成为能让明日放心的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事情要拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好保护这个孩子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妈妈约定好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时明明约定要保护明日的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却什么也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.00,0:08:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心了 真对不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好 连明日身体不舒服都没发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这次换我来照顾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经度过危险期了 应该没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要进行各种检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 明日会不会想吃苹果呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是什么也做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日不在我什么也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样根本保护不了明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能行啊
