Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样了 已经能起来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比昨天好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 啊 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你削了苹果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐削的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你没把苹果放在盐水里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.50,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了 真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.00,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我什么也做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 房东先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 我已经好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是太谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了这里就交给我 你快去学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐走好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日 你要保护这个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的 我一定会保护她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让明日早点打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把吉他带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你准备在这里唱歌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊我是想唱 有什么不方便吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是医院 别人会生气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.60,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很想听一之仓先生的歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得听了之后会变精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然明日都这么说了 那我就唱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飒飒清风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}缓缓地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒲公英
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈最喜欢的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我摘些去给病房的妈妈看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈每次看到蒲公英都会笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以拿去的话妈妈一定会好起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天每天摘花去病房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈 我又摘了花给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.50,0:15:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是什么也做不到 什么也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又为我摘蒲公英来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.20,0:15:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我什么也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.30,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明跟你约好的却...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到今天你摘的蒲公英
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一下子好像忘记自己生病了似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的笑容看起来好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你为什么看到蒲公英就会笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.40,0:16:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为蒲公英看起来很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.80,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快乐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.90,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为蒲公英跟今日一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.80,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒲公英跟今日一样好像总在微笑似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我看到蒲公英就会笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.50,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 妈妈不是看到蒲公英而笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在注视着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到我的笑容妈妈才绽放笑颜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在注视着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.00,0:16:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却…对明日总是摆出一脸痛苦的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不是谁的替身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就是姐姐 保持现在的样子就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道 姐姐就在这里 哪里也不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.40,0:17:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能为明日所作的唯一的一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为照顾我而累坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住院费又贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是觉得我很麻烦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日要早点康复哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的笑容就像蒲公英一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你出院了 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出院后好好休息一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.10,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间有劳你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了姐姐 我想去个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后可别忍着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 其实只是一开始是姐姐感冒更重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人有点不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以也没顾上自己的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.20,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.50,0:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 妈妈拜托了我一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.30,0:19:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前 在这个地方听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你姐姐 你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.20,0:20:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的声音和妈妈的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 也请保护你的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.90,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说要我保护姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是明日应该不记得妈妈的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是没有什么印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得听到过好多次这句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我和妈妈约定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我会的 我会保护姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会遵守约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建了40年的一间没有浴室的破烂小屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 春天到来的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你快看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 樱花盛开了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们非常幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐 这下糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱花满屋子飞

